<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <title>LMS Activation Email</title>
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <style type="text/css">
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: #FAFAFA;
            color: #222
        }

        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1.25;
            margin: 0px 0px 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin: 0px 0px 24px;
        }

        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        /* Layout */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: #fff
        }

        .email-header {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        /* button */
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to Elearning</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="email-body">
        <p>Hello <%=user.name %>
        </p>
        <p>Thank you for registering with Elearning. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:
        </p>
        <h2>
            <%= activationCode %>
        </h2>
        <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes.</p>
        <p>If you did not register for UTEDEMY account, please ignore this email. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="email-footer">
        <p>If you have any questions, please do not hestaite connect us at <a
                href="mailto:phantancuong2002@gmail.com">phantancuong2002@gmail.com</a></p>
    </div>
</body>

</html>